## Analysis Factors

### Shift Impact
- Morning shifts reduce sleep flexibility
- Evening shifts increase mental fatigue
- Night shifts increase recovery pressure

### Sleep Monitoring
- Late sleep hours reduce recovery
- Consecutive sleep imbalance increases alert probability

### Caffeine Tracking
Work shifts may include:
- 2 Turkish coffees
- 2x180ml Americano
- Additional caffeine support possible

Off-days:
- Reduced caffeine monitoring

